{
  "stem": "21550.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was always a step ahead of him, luckily.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- so he sat down in the garden, and started a conversation with a neighbor, who was at the window.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And guess what they talked about?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The best thing Hitler could do is get rid of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we listened to this here conversation, and we felt very, very bad about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When finally they came home, he said to them, there's something funny going on here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tried to get in, and I felt like the door was locked right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I went to the window, and-- and the windows were all locked.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Step ahead of me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She said, oh-- she wouldn't admit to anything, of course.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And something they [? wish ?] [? the ?] [? thing ?] up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they start talking about Hitler, what Hitler did good, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, at the beginning, there were the two of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my-- my brother-in-law came, and my-- my sister came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mala was the courier.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, there were-- there was a Polish government in exile in London.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a government inside, inside Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they both have-- had armies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They both had an underground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The one sponsored by the government in London was legitimate government, Polish government which escaped from Poland to England.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they helped the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They even dropped money to help people who didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they had the list of people whom they supported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other-- the other group had in their manifestor, I should say, that after the war, there would be no room for Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
